kabasuji.model

Class LightningLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • kabasuji.model.Level
      • kabasuji.model.LightningLevel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class LightningLevel
extends Level
    This class extends Level class to get the shared logic between the different types of levels. It contains the specific lightning level logic for example the timer information.
    Author:
    Ethan
